h3#events Events
p
	| The main widget's actions trigger custom events, which you can suscribe to execute any action.
p
	| Here is an example of the 
	code ready
	|  event, triggered when component ends its load process:
pre
	|foo.on("ready", function () {
	| 	var that = this; // Where "this" is the returned object of component
	| });
p
	| You can see the complete list of events in 
	a(href="/api/#{version}/symbols/ch.#{capital}.html#events-detail") #{friendly} API documentation
	| .
p
	| Learn more about events on our 
	a(href="/guides/use-callback-functions") step-by-step guide
	| .